  "description": "Hithink RoyalFlush Information Network Co., Ltd. provides internet financial information services in China and internationally. It operates through Value-Added Telecommunications Services, Software Sales and Maintenance, Advertising and Internet Business Promotion Services, and Fund Agent Sale and Other Trading Service segments. The company offers AI-powered financial information services; online trading software; system construction and maintenance; financial data; intelligent promotion services; financial news services; investment and wealth management analysis tools; wealth management product trading services; investment community exchange services; AI application products; investment research support and decision support systems; data terminals and interface services; and intelligent marketing solutions, as well as supplies online securities trading systems. It also provides computer application, fund consignment, private equity fund management, investment and consulting, insurance brokerage, technical, and medical device operations services. In addition, the company is involved in the corporate credit reporting business. It serves securities companies, fund companies, banks, insurance institutions, government departments, research institutions, listed companies, and individual investors. Hithink RoyalFlush Information Network Co., Ltd. was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Hangzhou, China.",
